<h6 id="toc0"><span>WORLD NEWS</span></h6>
<h1 id="toc1"><span>Putting an End to Restless Dreams</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc2"><span>A Nightmare's reign of terror came to a sudden conclusion last solar cycle with a surprise intervention from the Oneiroi West! Oneiroi West's populace is still recovering from this attack, but is hopeful about the future.</span></h2>
